01:08:03.910 --> 01:08:07.270
there's some great products
that Google has coming out

01:08:07.270 --> 01:08:09.210
that I'm excited about.

01:08:09.210 --> 01:08:13.040
A lot of the cloud services
and the ability to network

01:08:13.040 --> 01:08:16.170
with people and have video
conferencing are huge

01:08:16.170 --> 01:08:16.970
components for us.

01:08:16.970 --> 01:08:20.359
If we could have greater access
to video chat, that

01:08:20.359 --> 01:08:22.139
would be a huge thing.

01:08:22.139 --> 01:08:24.950
The other thing is cameras.

01:08:24.950 --> 01:08:31.770
We need to find a tech company
that can make a smaller

01:08:31.770 --> 01:08:35.640
smaller type of audio-recording
device.

01:08:35.640 --> 01:08:37.790
We have memory so small.

01:08:37.790 --> 01:08:40.810
Wouldn't it make sense to make a
microphone really small that

01:08:40.810 --> 01:08:43.470
could grab all the
audio properly?

01:08:43.470 --> 01:08:46.710
Because the audio becomes key
with law enforcement and

01:08:46.710 --> 01:08:49.220
getting the warrant to
rescue the victim.

01:08:49.220 --> 01:08:53.100
But we have cell phone
technologies which have

01:08:53.100 --> 01:08:54.170
advanced tremendously.

01:08:54.170 --> 01:08:58.330
And in New York, the New York
Police Department, they

01:08:58.330 --> 01:09:02.880
subpoenaed my video and my audio
recordings from one of

01:09:02.880 --> 01:09:04.369
our investigations.

01:09:04.369 --> 01:09:08.240
The pimp was beating her up
and was caught on camera.

01:09:08.240 --> 01:09:10.979
The use of technology from the
street corner gets her

01:09:10.979 --> 01:09:12.080
getting beat up.

01:09:12.080 --> 01:09:15.939
He goes into jail, and then
he gets out of jail.

01:09:15.939 --> 01:09:18.100
And I'm on the way to her, to
try to get to her at the

01:09:18.100 --> 01:09:21.800
shelter, but he gets
to her first.

01:09:21.800 --> 01:09:25.090
If we had the right kind of
technology, communication set

01:09:25.090 --> 01:09:27.310
up between the shelters, we
would have been able to

01:09:27.310 --> 01:09:30.260
intercede on that
victim's behalf.

01:09:30.260 --> 01:09:35.430
So most of the relationship with
tech companies has been

01:09:35.430 --> 01:09:38.450
to show the problem online,
whether it was

01:09:38.450 --> 01:09:39.939
Craiglist or Backpage.

01:09:39.939 --> 01:09:42.640
But in terms of companies that
are making products that are

01:09:42.640 --> 01:09:44.270
functional in the
investigation--

01:09:44.270 --> 01:09:46.600
of course Apple and Google.

01:09:46.600 --> 01:09:50.920
And I would like to see them
take a bigger role not just in

01:09:50.920 --> 01:09:53.540
discussing this subject
intellectually or funding more

01:09:53.540 --> 01:09:57.030
studies, but actually developing
technologies that

01:09:57.030 --> 01:10:01.590
will enable us to camera a room
and get audio and video

01:10:01.590 --> 01:10:04.840
in a way where it doesn't
require an entire army of

01:10:04.840 --> 01:10:08.350
wires and components
in the next room.

01:10:08.350 --> 01:10:11.240
We're still in the Dark Ages,
a little bit, on the

01:10:11.240 --> 01:10:11.910
technology.

01:10:11.910 --> 01:10:14.700
And I know that the
technology exists.

01:10:14.700 --> 01:10:19.330
So I don't have a sponsorship
with a tech company.

01:10:19.330 --> 01:10:22.510
I've worked against a number
of the platforms that the

01:10:22.510 --> 01:10:24.400
victims are being sold on.

01:10:24.400 --> 01:10:26.060
And I've seen other companies
step forward

01:10:26.060 --> 01:10:27.970
and start doing things.

01:10:27.970 --> 01:10:29.870
For example, Hersey,
there was an issue

01:10:29.870 --> 01:10:30.950
with chocolate slavery.

01:10:30.950 --> 01:10:35.190
But they're starting to look at
ways to utilize technology

01:10:35.190 --> 01:10:38.780
in the Ivory Coast and in Ghana
to better monitor what's

01:10:38.780 --> 01:10:41.850
going on on the thousands of
farms and whatnot, to sort of

01:10:41.850 --> 01:10:42.640
try to intervene.

01:10:42.640 --> 01:10:46.240
So I think that the traffickers
are ahead of the

01:10:46.240 --> 01:10:49.970
tech companies, because they
get the products first and

01:10:49.970 --> 01:10:53.970
begin utilizing them before the
tech companies have them

01:10:53.970 --> 01:10:57.210
in the hands of the human
rights activists.

01:10:57.210 --> 01:11:03.113
[APPLAUSE]

